INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (16, 1, '2012-05-16 06:27:36', '2012-05-16 06:27:36', '<!--:fr-->La fondation dâentreprise Bel a le souhait de soutenir des projets Ã©manant d\'associations basÃ©es Ã  travers le monde.\r\n\r\nVous reprÃ©sentez une association qui Åuvre pour le bien-Ãªtre des enfants et vous avez un projet en lien avec la promotion de modes dâalimentation Ã©quilibrÃ©s ?\r\n<div style="border: solid 2px #9B0;">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>TÃ©lÃ©chargez le <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/fr/pdf/Fondation_d-entreprise_Bel_Dossier_de_demande_de_soutien.doc">dossier de demande de soutien</a> et retournez-le complÃ©tÃ©, par email Ã  l\'adresse :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">contact@fondation-bel.org</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Les dossiers seront Ã©tudiÃ©s au fil de leur rÃ©ception dÃ¨s le mois de juillet 2012,<br />\r\net jusqu\'au 10 septembre 2012 au plus tard.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/warning.jpg" alt="" width="19" height="16" align="absmiddle" />Tout dossier incomplet ne pourra Ãªtre Ã©tudiÃ©.<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/warning.jpg" alt="" width="19" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nAvant dâÃªtre soumis au Conseil dâAdministration de laÂ <strong>Fondation</strong>, les dossiers sont prÃ©sÃ©lectionnÃ©s par le ComitÃ© de SÃ©lection et de Suivi des Projets (CSSP), aprÃ¨s analyse de plusieurs critÃ¨res.Â Parmi eux :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>La structure doit Ãªtre une<strong>Â association</strong>Â ou unÂ <strong>organisme Ã  but non lucratif</strong></li>\r\n	<li>LeÂ <strong>projet</strong>Â est spÃ©cifiquement liÃ© aux<strong>Â enfants</strong>Â (de 0 Ã  16 ans)</li>\r\n	<li>Le soutien concerne la rÃ©alisation concrÃ¨te dâune initiative, et non le financement de la structure ou de ses activitÃ©s courantes</li>\r\n	<li>Le<strong>Â projet</strong>Â sâinscrit dans la durÃ©e et Ã  vocation Ã  Ãªtre pÃ©renne</li>\r\n	<li>Le projet est basÃ© dans un des pays dans lesquels la Fondation intervient (<a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/fr/pdf/Pays%20dans%20lesquels%20la%20fondation%20intervient.pdf" target="_blank">voir la liste des pays</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Le CSSP se rÃ©unit autant de fois que nÃ©cessaire, et au minimum avant chaque Conseil dâAdministration. PrÃ©sidÃ© par Antoine FiÃ©vet, PrÃ©sident Directeur GÃ©nÃ©ral du groupe Bel, le Conseil dâAdministration de laÂ <strong>Fondation</strong>Â se rÃ©unit quant Ã  lui au minimum deux fois dans l\'annÃ©e pour donner son avis final sur les dossiers Ã  soutenir et pour suivre leur bonne exÃ©cution.</p><!--:--><!--:en-->The Bel Foundation\'s mission consist of supporting projects from associations based in countries all around the world.<br />\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you represent an association that works to improve children\'s well-being,Â </strong>and are you undertaking a project aimed atÂ <strong>promoting a balanced dietÂ ?</strong>\r\n\r\n<div style="border: solid 2px #9B0;">\r\n<p align="center"><strong>DownloadÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Bel_Foundation_Request_for_funding.doc">the application form</a>Â and send it back completed by email to the following address:</strong></p>\r\n<p align="center"><strong><a href="mailto:contact@fondation-bel.org">contact@fondation-bel.org</a></strong></p>\r\n<p align="center">Applications will be studied in the course of their receipt during July 2012<br />\r\nand till the week of September 10 at the latest.</p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/warning.jpg" alt="" width="19" height="16" align="absmiddle" />Â No incomplete files will be considered.<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/warning.jpg" alt="" width="19" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Before going to the Foundation\'s Board of Directors, applications are pre-selected by the Selection and Project Follow-up Committee (CSSP) after being analyzed using several criteria. These criteria include the following requirements:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Structure must have a not-for-profit designation</li>\r\n<li>Project must be specifically related to children (0-16 years of age)</li>\r\n<li>Grant must apply to actual implementation of an initiative and not to the association funding</li>\r\n<li>Project must be in line with long-term goals and have long-term durability</li>\r\n<li>Project must be based in one of the countries where the Foundation operates (<a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Countries%20where%20the%20Foundation%20operates.pdf">see the list of countries</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Selection and Project Follow-up Committee meets as many times as is necessary and at least before each Board of Directors meeting. Chaired by Antoine FiÃ©vet, Bel\'s Foundation Board of Directors meets twice a year to give its final decision on which cases should be sponsored and to follow up on them.</p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:fr-->Soumettre un projet<!--:--><!--:en-->Submit a project<!--:-->', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'soumettre_projet', '', '', '2012-07-12 16:29:17', '2012-07-12 15:29:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/05/bel/?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (18, 1, '2012-05-16 06:27:51', '2012-05-16 06:27:51', '<!--:fr-->Tous les jours, par le partage de l\'enthousiasme et du sourire, Bel et chacun de ses collaborateurs ont la conviction que de petites initiatives collectives peuvent gÃ©nÃ©rer de magnifiques succÃ¨s. Nous souhaitons que notre Fondation soit Ã  l\'image de notre entreprise et qu\'elle existe aussi grÃ¢ce Ã  vous !\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" />Â <a href="#">Soumettant une demande de soutien Ã  la Fondation</a>\r\n<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" />Â <a href="#">Mettant la Fondation en relation avec une association que vous connaissez</a>\r\n<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" />Â <a href="#">Parlant des activitÃ©s de la Fondation autour de vous</a></p>\r\n<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/script_fondation.gif" alt="La fondation d\'entreprise Bel est aussi la votre" width="346" height="42" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Soumettre une demande de soutien Ã  la Fondation</h2>\r\nLes bourses collaborateurs\r\n\r\n<strong>Vous pouvez vous impliquer dans la Fondation par le biais de bourses collaborateurs attribuÃ©es une fois par an.</strong> Lors du Conseil dâAdministration dâoctobre, jusquâÃ  10 bourses dâun montant de 5 000â¬ chacune sont en effet remises Ã  des projets proposÃ©s par des collaborateurs.\r\n<h2>Les critÃ¨res de sÃ©lection des projets</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ãtre proposÃ© par une Ã©quipe de collaborateurs Bel (minimum 2-3)</li>\r\n	<li>Ãtre basÃ© dans vos pays : concerner le lieu oÃ¹ les collaborateurs travaillent</li>\r\n	<li>Ãtre en faveur de<strong> lâenfance et de son bien-Ãªtre</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Ãtre au profit dâune <strong>association</strong> ou d\'un <strong>organisme Ã  but non lucratif</strong> fiable et pÃ©renne</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Comment soumettre un dossier de demande de bourse?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Pour les collaborateurs basÃ©s au SiÃ¨ge du Groupe</strong> : remplir le <a href="#">dossier de demande de bourse</a> et lâenvoyer par email Ã  <a href="contact@fondation-bel.org">contact@fondation-bel.org</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pour les collaborateurs sur site :</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Le collaborateur envoie par email le dossier de demande de bourse complÃ©tÃ© Ã  contact@fondation-bel.org.\r\nPour les collaborateurs ne disposant par dâun accÃ¨s Internet, le dossier peut Ãªtre envoyÃ© par courrier Ã  :\r\nFondation dâentreprise Bel\r\n16, boulevard Malesherbes\r\n75008 Paris â France</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Le dossier doit Ãªtre complÃ©tÃ© en FranÃ§ais ou Anglais. Pour les collaborateurs ne parlant aucune de ces deux langues, un autre contact sur site (Ã  dÃ©finir par le directeur du site) pourra gÃ©rer la relation avec la Fondation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Les dossiers seront Ã©tudiÃ©s au fil de leur rÃ©ception durant le mois de juillet 2012, et jusqu\'au 15 octobre au plus tard.</strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Mettre la Fondation en relation avec une association que vous connaissez</h2>\r\nTransmettez lui le <a href="#">dossier de demande de soutien</a> dÃ©diÃ© aux associations, ainsi que le <a href="#">rapport d\'activitÃ©</a> de la Fondation, ou dirigez-la vers le site de la Fondation : <a href="#">www.fondation-bel.org</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Parler des activitÃ©s de la Fondation autour de vous</h2>\r\n<strong>Un autre moyen de vous impliquer dans la Fondation consiste Ã  en parler autour de vous.</strong> Pour cela, le site Internet <a href="#">www.fondation-bel.org</a>, le <a href="#">rapport d\'activitÃ©</a> ainsi que <a href="#">le dossier de demande de soutien</a> dÃ©diÃ© aux associations, sont Ã  votre disposition.<!--:--><!--:en-->Each day, by sharing enthusiasm and smiles, Bel and its employees act on their conviction that small community initiatives can yield spectacular success. We would like our Foundation to embody the spirit of our company and to also exist thanks to you!\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" /></strong>Â <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/bel-employees/bel-employees-submit-a-project.html#1">Submitting an application form</a>\r\n<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" />Â <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/bel-employees/bel-employees-submit-a-project.html#2">Putting the Fondation in touch with an association of your acquaintance</a>\r\n<img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche_small.gif" alt="" width="18" height="14" align="absmiddle" />Â <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/bel-employees/bel-employees-submit-a-project.html#3">Talking about the Fondation\'s activities among yourselves</a></p>\r\n<strong></strong><img class="aligncenter" src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/en/script_fondation_en.gif" alt="" width="300" height="34" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Submit an application form</h2>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #99cc00;">Employee grants</span></h2>\r\n<strong>You can get involved in the Foundation through employee grants allocated once a year</strong>. At the October Board meeting, up to ten employee grants of â¬5,000 each are awarded to projects proposed by teams of employees.\r\n<h2>Projects selection criteria</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Be proposed by a team of Bel employeesÂ (minimum 2-3 people)</li>\r\n	<li>Be in your country: relate to the employees location</li>\r\n	<li>Be in favor of children and their well-being</li>\r\n	<li>Be in favor of a reliable and permanent association or non-profit organization</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How to submit a form ?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>For employees based at Group headquarters:Â </strong><a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Bel_Foundation_Employee_grant_request.doc">complete the application form</a>Â and email it toÂ <a href="mailto:contact@fondation-bel.org">contact@fondation-bel.org</a>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For employees based at a site:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The employee who supports the project emails theÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Bel_Foundation_Employee_grant_request.doc">completed application</a>Â to<a href="mailto:contact@fondation-bel.org">contact@fondation-bel.org</a>.For employees who do not have an Internet access, the application can be posted to:Fondation dâentreprise Bel\r\n\r\n16, bd Malesherbes\r\n\r\n75008 Paris â France</li>\r\n	<li>The application must be completed in French or in English. For employees who do not speak either of these languages, another contact person on the site (to be chosen by the site director) will be able to liaise with the Foundation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><strong>Applications will be studied in the course of their receipt during July 2012 and till the week of October 15 at the latest.</strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Put the Foundation in touch with an association of your acquaintance</h2>\r\nSubmit theÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Bel_Foundation_Request_for_funding.doc">application form</a>Â dedicated to associations to your contact, as well as theÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/publications.html">Foundation progress report</a>Â or lead it to the Foundation web site:Â <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/" target="_blank">www.fondation-bel.org</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img src="http://www.fondation-bel.org/images/fleche.gif" alt="" width="69" height="45" align="absmiddle" />Talking about the Foundation among yourselves</h2>\r\n<strong><strong>Another way for you to get invoved in the Foundation is to talk about it among yourselves.Â </strong></strong>In this regard, the internet siteÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/" target="_blank">www.fondation-bel.org</a>, theÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/publications.html">Progress Report</a>Â and theÂ <a href="http://www.fondation-bel.org/en/pdf/Bel_Foundation_Request_for_funding.doc">application form</a>Â dedicated to associations, are available to you.<!--:-->', '<!--:fr-->Collaborateurs Bel<!--:en-->Bel\'s collaboraters<!--:-->', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'collaborateurs-bel', '', '', '2012-07-12 12:15:52', '2012-07-12 11:15:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/05/bel/?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
